data.description: Seller to contribute $6000 towards Closing! This highly desired multi-gen home has 2 homes under one roof! This stunning property offers an open & upgraded split floorplan! The main home features a wide entryway, full den with closet (could be used as a 3rd bedroom). Wood-look tile throughout, upgraded carpet in bedrooms, blinds and ceiling fans. The spacious great room, kitchen, and dining room all overlook the backyard with desert & MOUNTAIN VIEWS!! Both kitchens feature stainless steel appliances, sparkling white quartz countertops and white cabinets with modern pulls. Luxurious owner's suite features dual vanity, large rain shower, walk-in closet, and convenient patio access! Additional bedroom and secondary bathroom located down the hall in a split design that promotes privacy. Attached private casita features a separate front entrance, large bedroom w/walk-in closet, laundry, living area, full kitchen, private patio, and private 1 car garage! Sit back and enjoy gorgeous AZ sunsets from main house's private backyard or relax in the spa. Entertain your guests by grilling up your favorite meal on the built in BBQ while they relax by the outdoor firepit. Estrella community features parks, fitness centers, lakes for boating & fishing, hiking and is home to a Nicklaus-designed championship golf course. You CAN live the dream here!
